---
title: Sticky Indian-Style Chickpea Tacos with Cucumber, Tomato Salad & Yoghurt
description: Flavour-fusion tacos might be one of our favourites and oh boy, do we have a twist for you tonight! Filled with spiced chickpeas, crunchy cucumber and a cooling dollop of yoghurt, these are a fun, mixed-up feast that’ll spice up your taco game.
